**update**

as mention by [a_local_nobody][1] it is worth mentioning that [first][2] will throw an `NoSuchElementException` but [firstOrNull][3] will return `null`


  [1]: https://stackoverflow.com/users/4729721/a-local-nobody
  [2]: https://kotlinlang.org/api/latest/jvm/stdlib/kotlin.collections/first.html
